      • Property Summary

        Properties 
        Name Description
        Identifier
        An identifier used to uniquely reference an object in a system (e.g. an airline reservation reference, customer profile reference, booking confirmation number, or a reference to a previous availability quote).
        Details
        Type http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:Identifier
        Example Value guid12345
        Required true
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        OtherID
        These identifiers are assigned by systems other than the system that generated this record.
        Details
        Type http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:Identifier
        Example Value guid12345
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 5

        Example Value marriottCustomer_1
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
